# Keep the Docker build context small and deterministic: never ship local build
# output, VCS metadata, IDE files, or host-side data into the image.
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/publish/

.git/
.gitignore
.github/
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
**/*.user
**/*.suo

# Node / web tooling artifacts (if any wwwroot tooling is added later)
**/node_modules/

# Local data & secrets — must never bake into an image
**/projects.json
**/*.db
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm
.env
*.env

# Docs / CI that don't belong in the runtime image
*.md
docker-compose*.yml
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
